The paper discusses the use of memristors for optimization and machine learning problems, which falls under the category of emerging technologies (cs.ET). The paper also mentions the use of memristors for neural networks (cs.NE) and control systems (cs.SY). The focus on optimization and machine learning suggests that the paper may also be relevant to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC).
